<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="img/fav.png" />
  <title>Star Wars - Battle Quotes</title>
  
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/normalize/5.0.0/normalize.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0-beta.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-PsH8R72JQ3SOdhVi3uxftmaW6Vc51MKb0q5P2rRUpPvrszuE4W1povHYgTpBfshb"
    crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/starwars.css">


</head>

<body>



  <div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-md-center">
      <div class="col-md-3 txc">
        <div>
          <img src="img/logo.png" class="logo">
        </div>
        <div id="container" onmouseover="playclip();">


          <audio>
            <source src="music/hover.mp3">
            <source src="music/hover.ogg">
          </audio>
          <div id="sounddiv">
            <bgsound id="sound">
          </div>

          <div id="burger">
            <div class="bun top"></div>
            <div class="filling"></div>
            <div class="bun bottom"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row" style="position:absolute">
          <nav>
            <p>Hello great Padawan, after a long period of training, you must have learned a lot with Master Yoda, do you remember
              something he taught? Tell me down.</p>
            <form action="/quotes" method="POST">
              <input type="text" placeholder="name" name="name" value="Yoda" style="display: none">
              <input type="text" placeholder="Type here..." name="quote" class="campo" maxlength="70" required>
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg outline green">Speak  </button>
            </form>

            <p>Hmm I can feel a bad energy coming from you, we can not let happen what happened to Anakin Skywalke.
              <br>Do not let Darth Vader enter your mind!</p>
            <button id="update" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg outline red"> Listen to Darth Vader </button>

            <p>
              <br>Hurry, this is getting serious! Ask for help on the bright side of the force!
              <br>I hope you get well.</p>
            <button id="delete" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg outline blue"> Request Help  </button>

          </nav>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-9" style="padding-top:130px;">

        <ul class="quotes">
          <% for(var i=0; i<quotes.length; i++) {%>
            <div class="borda<%= quotes[i].name %> <%= quotes[i].name %>">
              <li class="quote">
                <span class="name">
                  <%= quotes[i].name %>
                </span>
                <br>
                <span class="fala">
                  <%= quotes[i].quote %>
                </span>

              </li>
            </div>
            <% } %>
        </ul>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-3 falas">

  </div>
  <div class="col-md-9">

  </div>
  </div>
  </div>

  <script src='http://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.1.3/jquery.min.js'></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="js/sound-mouseover.js"></script>
  <script src="js/starwars.js"></script>
  <script src="main.js"></script>
</body>

</html>